Package: einstein
Type: Package
Title: Syntactic Sugar for the Einstein Summation Convention
Version: 0.3
Date: 2014-10-26
Author: Martin Elff
Maintainer: Martin Elff <elff@gmx.com>
Description: This package intends to ease programming with multidemsional arrays by allowing
  an easy translation into R code of mathematical expressions using the Einstein 
  summation convention for tensor operations 
License: GPL
Depends: partitions